Rating: 3
This makes a great dish for vegetarians. Substitute Morningstar Farm's Meal Starters Steak Strips for the beef tenderloin. Defrost before using, skip the salt and pepper, and saute as directed. Both my husband and I missed having potatoes in the stew, so I roasted some to go alongside. A winner.

